EXPRESSION: CASE WHEN COALESCE(DATEOFBIRTH,'') = '' THEN timestamp'1000-01-03 00:00:00.000GMT+7' ELSE  to_timestamp( SUBSTR(DATEOFBIRTH,1,4)||'-'||SUBSTR(DATEOFBIRTH,5,2)||'-'||SUBSTR(DATEOFBIRTH,7,2)||' '|| SUBSTR(DATEOFBIRTH,10,2)||':'||SUBSTR(DATEOFBIRTH,12,2)||':'||SUBSTR(DATEOFBIRTH,14,2) ) + INTERVAL '7' HOUR END
